{
  "title": "pdfsignerpy: digitally sign and verify PDF documents (PAdES) with a pure-Rust backend",
  "description": "Python bindings (PyO3) over the pure-Rust pdf_signer engine to digitally sign and verify PDF documents with full PAdES (ETSI EN 319 142) support, from B-B to B-LTA. No Java, no OpenSSL, no external tools. Installed from PyPI as `pdfsignerpy` and imported as `pdfsigner`.",
